@startuml
title Project Architecture Diagram

actor User as U

rectangle "Search Agent\n(Uses Tavity tool for web search)" as SA
rectangle "Content Management Agent\nProcesses and filters data" as CMA
rectangle "Output/Tuning Agent\nTunes final content" as OTA

U -> SA : Enter input text
SA -> CMA : Provide search results
CMA -> OTA : Filtered & processed content
OTA -> U : Final output

@enduml
